#Please use the following instructions to test the basic functionality of nano:
#Go to a testing directory.

$ nano <new_file>

#Inside nano insert some text and then use the instructions at the bottom of the screen to save, copy, cut, etc.

#Other tests may include:
# - opening a file with the cursor on a specific line and character (if character number is omitted, the cursor will be positioned on the first character):
$ nano +<line_number>,<character_number> <file_name>
